<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Meine Geschichtenwelt</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffecd2, #fcb69f);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        header {
            padding: 2rem;
            background-color: #ffffff88;
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ffb347;
        }
        header h1 {
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }
        header p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #555;
        }
        .language-selection {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin: 3rem 0;
        }
        .language-button {
            padding: 1.5rem 3rem;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            background-color: #ffb347;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .language-button:hover {
            background-color: #ff9966;
        }
        main {
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        footer {
            margin-top: 3rem;
            padding: 1rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Meine Geschichtenwelt</h1>
        <p>Welcome to my writing world / Willkommen in meiner Schreib-Welt</p>
    </header>

    <section class="language-selection">
        <button class="language-button" onclick="location.href='geschichten-de.html'">Deutsch</button>
        <button class="language-button" onclick="location.href='geschichten-en.html'">English</button>
    </section>

    <main>
        <h2>Entdecke bald meine Geschichten!</h2>
        <p>Hier findest du bald spannende Kurzgeschichten in deiner Lieblingssprache.</p>
    </main>

    <footer>
        &copy; 2025 Deine Geschichtenwelt
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
